			<p class="absolute top-65 w-full text-white text-6xl font-bold italic z-20 text-center px-4">
				<span class="text-[#e63946]">S</span>ILKSONG <span class="text-[#e63946]">S</span>PEEDRUNNING <span class="text-[#e63946]">S</span>TRATS
