			</p>
			<div class="hover:bg-white cursor-pointer animate-bounce hover:text-black transition-colors duration-400 absolute top-120 tracking-widest left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 h-15 w-55 justify-center items-center font-bold flex flex-col border-1 border-white text-white top-50 z-50">WHERE TO START?</div>
		</div>
	</div>
